{"tid":2497070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本港新增８宗確診，其中一宗4月6日經東莞回港易回港人士，當本地感染","createTime":"2021-04-20T09:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T11:45:43.000Z","uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"025f39564345c686f0aeb2d71e63f0292f5ad758","tid":2497070,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:07:10.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社２０日專訊》衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，截至４月２０日零時零分，本港新增８宗新冠肺炎確診個案，涉及２男６女，３宗為輸入個案，４宗本地個案，１宗仍有待分類。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">其中一宗本地個案涉及一名４６歲女患者，她是回港易人士，住青山公路荃灣新青大廈，４月６日經深圳灣東莞回港，４月１０至１９日到荃灣如心酒店任房務員執房，４月１９日最後上班。</span><br />\n至於３宗輸入個案，包括兩名印度來港２歲幼兒，另一個菲律賓來港女子帶有Ｎ５０１Ｙ變種病毒。（ｃｌ）"},{"pid":"17abed695c8c96fab2dbd8144ed1a774bf2dbdff","tid":2497070,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"啱啱好14日潛伏期，又當本地？"},{"pid":"368d0a6f59b2ef91a4d9882b2b7cb9b2907aa387","tid":2497070,"uid":290372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"支拿唔係清左零咩?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d264441577bace5c9a679380f2ce917abbbe684b","tid":2497070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752e3a61ac305a62e5a216ea4ea3f4739231bf48","tid":2497070,"uid":4155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"又係荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5683d751e22